source.title: West-Saxon Gospels
source.editor: The text was imported from the York-Toronto-Helsinki Parsed Corpus of Old English Prose (YCOE), including the morphological annotation. Further morphological annotation was then added, including lemmatization. The syntactic annotation is independent of YCOE. Documentation for the morphological and syntactic annotation can be found here: http://folk.uio.no/krisbec/OE_guidelines.pdf
source.annotator: Kristin Bech (816 sentences), Kari Haugland (537 sentences), and Hanne Eckhoff (2 sentences)
source.reviewer: Kristin Bech (1354 sentences) and Hanne Eckhoff (1 sentence)
